    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Our service</h2>
        <p>We ensure safe payment for customer and safe cash on delivery service as well. We are here to provide your product next to your door. We are known for our premium services. Offering customers free servicing ensuring a next-level experience.</p>

    </div>
</div>